Package com.im.njams.sdk.logmessage

Class ActivityBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.im.njams.sdk.logmessage.ActivityBuilder
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GroupBuilder
    public class ActivityBuilder
extends Object
    This Builder will be used to create activities. To get this Builder, use the start function on the Job Object or the stepTo function on the previously created Activity.
    Author:
    stkniep
